{"tid":430590,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無手足有過膕窩肌拉傷？","createTime":"2017-10-10T02:31:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-10T06:08:18.000Z","uid":8598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5466fff5947b064f817efbea3dd2a9cad414adee","tid":430590,"uid":8598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T02:31:22.000Z","msg":"示意圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/10/095823_df320b85768c04769467674a9d2bd9fc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F10%2F095823_df320b85768c04769467674a9d2bd9fc.jpg&h=d6a44966&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n自己有做開運動要經常起跳，早一個月前因腳有傷口費事掂水，所以沖涼時要單腳企，再加上揸細電單車車要摺腳，令到上圖綠色位置受壓，所以我懷疑以上兩種原因令到我惡化個情況<br />\n<br />\n有無啲咩方法可以減輕痛楚？有時隻腳摺太耐，一企喺身隻腳就好酸軟，要gut 幾吓先回復正常咁<br />\n<br />\n又或者睇醫生，應該睇咩分科？或者巿面上有咩地方可以睇吓有關運動創傷嘅症？事關我膊頭又有啲suck<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">ching你好</span></span>"},{"pid":"db5f89c317e79a1f70f5324292a0a113009efd91","tid":430590,"uid":8598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T02:37:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0d1f49c88381e4bb6cb3d699608f7963a27803cf","tid":430590,"uid":8598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T02:39:22.000Z","msg":"無人受傷"},{"pid":"aad7cfa4b9f7670eabfb51abc280e20a2134971f","tid":430590,"uid":8598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T02:41:46.000Z","msg":"好橙"},{"pid":"e6e2d28678b8c300bd5401ef76a14a03748c4c41","tid":430590,"uid":22876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T02:44:50.000Z","msg":"你分到邊舊肌肉痛<br />\n同估到痛症成因<br />\n已經專業過呢到9成9連登仔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我諗都係日拉夜拉筋<br />\n再得佢自己好返啦"},{"pid":"1a0135a395e4bed9d92cf1f6e4c942569fab4b1c","tid":430590,"uid":51758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T02:45:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fe6b010bce222524e992bb020a43ffbe30f5cece","tid":430590,"uid":51758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T02:51:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fbd8c6e8cb92f0977a0c2add5587c9f8581f36d8","tid":430590,"uid":8598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T02:51:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你分到邊舊肌肉痛<br />\n同估到痛症成因<br />\n已經專業過呢到9成9連登仔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我諗都係日拉夜拉筋<br />\n再得佢自己好返啦</blockquote><br />\n多謝你，依家晚晚都拉"},{"pid":"c1205d234fea811d86824865c4afa24ec0249afc","tid":430590,"uid":8598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T02:53:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有機會係股骨內旋 傾向用外側肌肉<br />\n消左炎先 再伸展 然後練下內側 改善用力平衡<br />\n<br />\n利申：trainer</blockquote><br />\n大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  話說我有O 形腳，聽你咁形容，我覺得好中<br />\n但我可以點樣改善？真心求教"},{"pid":"71350d78497ac47420d6d37e29d6e71f9c0505cf","tid":430590,"uid":8598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T02:54:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>消炎&lt; 有買保險就睇物理治療<br />\n但唔好預斷到尾 因為你會keep住做運動<br />\n你用力習慣差 只會一直翻發</blockquote><br />\n消炎只有食藥呢一著嗎？有無藥go 可以代替？"},{"pid":"c8f8be97cbf60e5a558826de66e3f1fa47fd2e7c","tid":430590,"uid":8598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T03:06:38.000Z","msg":"Little puss"},{"pid":"1e2b16e96c6485f04a3ae52e0f59c9bf074bb903","tid":430590,"uid":46911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T03:09:06.000Z","msg":"我近排都拉傷左個膊頭<br />\n但我分唔到係筋鍵定肌肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"619675de38af37d8b4a3da87ab1e65e5be222895","tid":430590,"uid":51758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T03:11:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1e80457888619ffc72d68a86685dc9fc7da84080","tid":430590,"uid":13841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T03:16:16.000Z","msg":"得閑就敷下冰，休息下做少啲運動<br />\n過一兩個星期等佢消左炎唔痛再拉筋拉返鬆佢"},{"pid":"a15625967e154186f66c1cf90ca551efee33c1fa","tid":430590,"uid":51758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T03:19:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6f4fac9a0c9564a5428e85b1ad8890486af37eb3","tid":430590,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T03:33:53.000Z","msg":"睇左窩腹肌拉面"},{"pid":"2f7dedad815061e3cb69d40059dde7185cadcc58","tid":430590,"uid":8598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T03:58:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有機會係股骨內旋 傾向用外側肌肉<br />\n消左炎先 再伸展 然後練下內側 改善用力平衡<br />\n<br />\n利申：trainer</blockquote><br />\n大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  話說我有O 形腳，聽你咁形容，我覺得好中<br />\n但我可以點樣改善？真心求教</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/10/110021_c9f0a6fd0599eb7b62774942065b8453.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F10%2F110021_c9f0a6fd0599eb7b62774942065b8453.jpg&h=729d1a41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n亦有機會係你做運動/單腳企 用唔到glute med，令到TFL /IT BAND過勞，最緊要對症下藥<br />\n<br />\nglute bridge /squat /sumo deadlift <br />\nadductors 同glute med都要練<br />\n當然啦 動作既performance好重要 做得唔好都有機會令自己惡化</blockquote><br />\n希望啦，我自己好著重姿勢，好姿勢可以令到做嗰個動作嘅效益最大，我會留意了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25b515c4e5a3d35e923ce3ca03455bb1a326b406","tid":430590,"uid":8598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T03:58:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得閑就敷下冰，休息下做少啲運動<br />\n過一兩個星期等佢消左炎唔痛再拉筋拉返鬆佢</blockquote><br />\n唯有係咁，但唔想休息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6a6a2145fe38e06ceb6cb0083e628f45c2cf25f","tid":430590,"uid":8598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T04:03:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>消炎&lt; 有買保險就睇物理治療<br />\n但唔好預斷到尾 因為你會keep住做運動<br />\n你用力習慣差 只會一直翻發</blockquote><br />\n消炎只有食藥呢一著嗎？有無藥go 可以代替？</blockquote><br />\n物理治療有聲波 冷凍/熱<br />\n消炎藥/膠布都ok <br />\n針灸 個人經驗就覺得無乜效率</blockquote><br />\n你有無啲咩消炎藥/tape 有推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac65fcf3ceb7f0cfff87d9bd4e7a473a44bf608c","tid":430590,"uid":42209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T04:10:51.000Z","msg":"lm 同樣痛法 準備睇物理治療"},{"pid":"5aec78235f119f9014b2551e336a2c4e474563ac","tid":430590,"uid":92456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T05:52:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>得閑就敷下冰，休息下做少啲運動<br />\n過一兩個星期等佢消左炎唔痛再拉筋拉返鬆佢</blockquote><br />\n唯有係咁，但唔想休息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔休息會好傷"},{"pid":"ba98bd3461224efd0fdec3356f2543e7523cf5f5","tid":430590,"uid":8598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T06:08:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>得閑就敷下冰，休息下做少啲運動<br />\n過一兩個星期等佢消左炎唔痛再拉筋拉返鬆佢</blockquote><br />\n唯有係咁，但唔想休息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔休息會好傷</blockquote><br />\n知道，過埋下星期一會休息了"}]}